Package election

Class FileParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • election.FileParser
  • public class FileParser
extends java.lang.Object
    This class conducts the parsing of an Election. It will parse all of the important information from a given election for the Election class

    • Method Detail

      • parse

        public static Election parse​(java.lang.String filePath,
                             java.lang.String outputPath,
                             java.lang.String fileName)
        This method parses the given election file to determine if it is an Instant Runoff election or an Open Party Listing election. The corresponding election parser method is then called. Invalid election types are caught with exceptions.
        Parameters:
        filePath - String containing the input path for the election file
        outputPath - String representing the desired output path for the media file
        fileName - String representing the desired name for the media file to be produced
        Returns:
        either a parsed IRElection object or a parsed OPLElection object, depending on the election type

      • parseIR

        public static IRElection parseIR​(java.util.Scanner scanner,
                                 java.lang.String outputPath,
                                 java.lang.String fileName)
        This method parses an Instant Runoff election.
        Parameters:
        scanner - Java I/O scanner object
        outputPath - the output path of any created files
        fileName - the name of the file to be created
        Returns:
        IRElection object, containing the final state of the election

        public static Ballot getBallot​(java.lang.String ballotLine,
                               int electionType,

        Parameters:
        ballotLine - a String representing the data line of the ballot
        electionType - an integer representing the type of the election, 0 for Instant Runoff and 1 for Open Party Listing
        ballotNum - an integer representing the ID number of the ballot
        Returns:

      • createParties
